  "text": "This process finds the matches between keypoints using the Euclidean distance between the corresponding descriptors. The nearest neighbor algorithm is utilized to match the descriptors. After getting the initial matching points, there are still many wrong matching points. The RANSAC algorithm [CITATION_1] is employed to rule out the wrong match point pairs.",
